frames.caption: A warrior clad in ornate armor stands prominently against a dramatic mountainous backdrop. The intricate gold detailing on his armor glistens in the warm, golden light of the setting sun. His horned helmet adds an imposing and mythical presence to the scene.

frames.caption: A warrior clad in ornate armor with horned helmet leads a group through a dusty, mountainous landscape.
